    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been assessed. Achieved levels meet required levels across all factors under the Low assurance framing for MRL 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification confirms hemolysis predictions remain below the absolute clinical threshold across the full uncertainty envelope. The assessment references supporting methodology described in the hemolysis CFD validation literature (including work cited via referencesIdentifier). The package is accepted as providing sufficient credibility evidence for the VAD COU.",
